	Document abort() bugs.
	* doc/posix-functions/abort.texi (abort): Mention anomalies.

	* doc/posix-functions/setjmp.texi (setjmp): Mingw has setjmp.
	* doc/posix-functions/sigsetjmp.texi (sigsetjmp): Cygwin has
	sigsetjmp.
