	gl_FUNC_ALLOCA no longer defines HAVE_ALLOCA_H unconditionally.
	See <http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/bug-gnulib/2007-12/msg00149.html>.
	* NEWS: announce this.
	* m4/alloca.m4 (gl_FUNC_ALLOCA): Don't define HAVE_ALLOCA_H.

