	* m4/getline.m4 (gl_FUNC_GETLINE): Require only autoconf-2.59.  2.60
	is not needed, since gnulib now permits use of AC_CHECK_DECLS_ONCE.
	* m4/getdelim.m4 (gl_FUNC_GETDELIM): Likewise.

