2007-06-22  Ralf Wildenhues  <Ralf.Wildenhues@gmx.de>

	* gnulib-tool (func_add_or_update, func_create_testdir): Do not
	simplify `sed_replace_build_aux' scripts, they are portable but
	echoing them with `echo' is not.
