	* m4/sys_socket_h.m4 (gl_HEADER_SYS_SOCKET): Likewise.
	* m4/sys_stat_h.m4 (gl_HEADER_SYS_STAT_H): Likewise.
	* m4/sys_time_h.m4 (gl_HEADER_SYS_TIME_H_BODY): Likewise.
	* m4/sysexits.m4 (gl_SYSEXITS): Likewise.
