	* m4/absolute-header.m4 (gl_ABSOLUTE_HEADER): Fix POSIX sed portability
	glitch reported by Ralf Wildenhues in
	<http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/bug-gnulib/2007-06/msg00114.html>.

