	Followup to the 2007-02-12 patch, using suggestions from Bruno Haible in
	<http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/bug-gnulib/2007-02/msg00136.html>.
	* doc/gnulib-tool.texi (Initial import): Mention _FILE_OFFSET_BITS
	as another example.
