	Require gl_HEADER_TIME_H_DEFAULTS.
	* m4/strptime.m4 (gl_FUNC_STRPTIME): Likewise.
	* m4/time_r.m4 (gl_TIME_R): Likewise.
	* m4/timegm.m4 (gl_FUNC_TIMEGM): Likewise.

