	* README: Advise users that they might find the bug-gnulib@gnu.org
	and autotools-announce@gnu.org mailing lists useful.

2006-11-28  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	* m4/ptrdiff_max.m4: Remove file.

