	* m4/eoverflow.m4 (gl_EOVERFLOW): Use AC_COMPUTE_INT instead of
	_AC_COMPUTE_INT.
	(AC_COMPUTE_INT): Add fallback definition for autoconf < 2.61.
	* m4/ptrdiff_max.m4 (gl_PTRDIFF_MAX): Use AC_COMPUTE_INT instead of
	_AC_COMPUTE_INT.
	(AC_COMPUTE_INT): Add fallback definition for autoconf < 2.61.
