	to pacify gcc -Wswitch-default.

2006-01-22  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	* lib/vasnprintf.c (VASNPRINTF): In the computation of the size of the
	temporary buffer for sprintf, take into account the precision also
	for 'd', 'i', 'u', 'o', 'x', 'X'.

