	* modules/stdint (License): Change to LGPL.

2005-10-04  Simon Josefsson  <jas@extundo.com>

	* lib/getaddrinfo.h: Move sys/types.h include first, reported by "Mark
	D. Baushke" <mdb@gnu.org>.

