	* lib/strcase.h (strcasecmp): Add note in comments.
	* lib/strncasecmp.c: Use code from strcasecmp.c.
	* lib/strcasecmp.c: Use mbchar module. Define private mbiter variant.
	(strcasecmp): Work correctly in multibyte locales.

