	* m4/lib-link.m4, lib-prefix.m4, nls.m4, po.m4, printf-posix.m4:
	* m4/progtest.m4:
	Update from GNU gettext 0.14.2.
	* m4/glibc2.m4: New file, from GNU gettext 0.14.2.

