2005-01-18  Bob Proulx  <bob@proulx.com>

	* lib/obstack.c [DEFAULT_ALIGNMENT]: Use an intermediate type to
	simplify offsetof() macro construct to avoid compile failure with
	native HP-UX 11.0 ANSI C compiler.

