	* lib/config.charset: update from gettext-runtime.

2003-12-03  Paul Eggert  <eggert@twinsun.com>

	* lib/getgroups.c (getgroups): xmalloc takes one argument, not two.
	Bug reported by Alfred M. Szmidt.

