	* m4/getloadavg.m4: Use [\t ], not [ \t] (where \t is a literal TAB).
	* m4/lib-ld.m4: Likewise.

2003-08-18  Jim Meyering  <jim@meyering.net>

	* lib/setenv.h: Indent nested cpp directive.
	* lib/vasnprintf.c: Remove trailing blanks.

