	* m4/dirfd.m4 (UTILS_FUNC_DIRFD): Fix a quoting bug leading to an
	invalid expansion for AC_EGREP_CPP.
	* m4/strtoimax.m4 (gl_FUNC_STRTOIMAX): Likewise.
