	* m4/memchr.m4: New file.

	Module memcmp.
	* m4/memcmp.m4 (gl_PREREQ_MEMCMP): New macro.
	(jm_FUNC_MEMCMP): Invoke it.

	Module memcpy.
	* m4/memcpy.m4: New file.

	Module memmove.
	* m4/memmove.m4: New file.

	Module memset.
	* m4/memset.m4: New file.

