2002-06-21  Jim Meyering  <meyering@lucent.com>

	* m4/c-bs-a.m4: Add comment, from diffutils-2.8.2.
	* m4/mbrtowc.m4: Likewise.

	* m4/mbstate_t.m4: Update from diffutils-2.8.2.
