	* lib/xgetcwd.c (xgetcwd) [defined __GLIBC__ && __GLIBC__ >= 2]:
	Simply `return getcwd (NULL, 0);'.
	[! (defined __GLIBC__ && __GLIBC__ >= 2)]:
	Use 1300 as initial value for length, not PATH_MAX.

	* lib/pathmax.h: Clean up cpp syntax.

