	(BUILT_SOURCES): Add unlocked-io.h.
	(io_functions): Define.
	(unlocked-io.h): New rule.
	(DISTCLEANFILES): Add unlocked-io.h.
	(all-local): Depend on unlocked-io.h, to ensure it is created.

	* lib/unlocked-io.hin: New file

	* lib/regex.c: Update from glibc.

