	* lib/config.charset: Add ISO-8859-3, BIG5HKSCS, GB18030, JOHAB,
	VISCII, CP874, CP949, CP950, CP1250, CP1253, CP1254, CP1255, CP1256,
	CP1257 to the list of canonical encodings. Rename EUC-CN to GB2312.

