2000-09-18  Jim Meyering  <meyering@lucent.com>

	* m4/getloadavg.m4 (AC_FUNC_GETLOADAVG): Restore the initial value of
	LIBS. Otherwise, everyone ends up linking with -lelf for some
	configurations.
	Reported by Mike Stone.

