	* lib/quotearg.c: Rename ISASCII to IN_CTYPE_DOMAIN, so people don't
	think it should be used as a general replacement for isascii.
	* lib/fnmatch.c: Likewise.
	* lib/mbswidth.c: Likewise
	* lib/regex.c: Likewise.

	Don't use atoi.
