	* m4/largefile.m4 (AC_SYS_LARGEFILE): Define _XOPEN_SOURCE to
	be 500, instead of _GNU_SOURCE to be 1, to work around glibc
	2.1.3 bug.  This avoids a clash when files like regex.c define
	_GNU_SOURCE.

